{"tid":1635983,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[提議] 放哨改進","createTime":"2019-10-07T15:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T01:18:55.000Z","uid":197379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b3311b62abced42e56783108b42d8ef1fd03ccea","tid":1635983,"uid":197379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:58:56.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post話屯門哨兵嚴重唔夠，今晚先咁多手足卑人拉<br />\n雖然而家好多地區都有tg哨group，但好多時update得唔夠及時，有時出左事先知有狗<br />\n<br />\n我建議每區set大概十到廿個哨點，請各哨兵長註自己個哨點，唔好周圍走<br />\n如果係個哨點開始放哨或者收工，就同哨group admin講<br />\nAdmin可以即時update各哨點狀況，例如<br />\n<br />\n哨點<br />\n地點A online<br />\n地點B online<br />\n地點C offline<br />\n<br />\n咁樣大家就可以肯定邊到人幫手實時睇緊，哨兵見邊個位冇人睇又可以補位，唔洗重疊咁嘥人 <br />\n<br />\n放哨消息比起而家一定會更全面，消息update得更快<br />\n<br />\n講咁多都係希望唔好再有手足卑人拉咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家覺得可以點改善放哨都講下呀"},{"pid":"3903a6086a2e689609a95fc9277f051450cec06e","tid":1635983,"uid":197379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:42:41.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"841db1124aafcef0df5338b656c3167b8a1918d8","tid":1635983,"uid":197379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"044aac5fa407234f931f81c61aa0269e9c594edc","tid":1635983,"uid":264697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a472bbfe315a684baf53f82fd4b08ed6606e7f75","tid":1635983,"uid":255092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"唔錯 推"},{"pid":"7273d2c3d56b320c5061bbcb1ddf2d6cda6194bc","tid":1635983,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:23:33.000Z","msg":"有固定位置，<br />\n驚唔驚哨兵手足會容易俾狗咬"},{"pid":"e2b1514a8d2eb0bf6932fef6c7c4fc90b3fbe05a","tid":1635983,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:26:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"62e61b7e000594243f0c0fcc639abee458204cc5","tid":1635983,"uid":197379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7273d2c3d56b320c5061bbcb1ddf2d6cda6194bc","tid":1635983,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:23:33.000Z","msg":"有固定位置，<br />\n驚唔驚哨兵手足會容易俾狗咬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:51:22.000Z","msg":"哨兵通常都街坊裝，正常就隱藏得幾好既<br />\n<br />\n同埋個哨點唔一定要好明確係邊棟大廈/邊個涼亭入面<br />\n<br />\n只需要大範圍啲，好似邊個公園或者邊個路口咁 <br />\n<br />\n周圍咁多街坊，應該好容易容入普通市民，冇咁易卑狗咬"},{"pid":"5c5801b66b8bc51b351a6703fa19c380d134c040","tid":1635983,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:54:56.000Z","msg":"哨兵好重要，<br />\n仲要留意經過既車"},{"pid":"826a92bd9870a4f89ab09d5ad7e4712e9c93ec74","tid":1635983,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e61b7e000594243f0c0fcc639abee458204cc5","tid":1635983,"uid":197379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7273d2c3d56b320c5061bbcb1ddf2d6cda6194bc","tid":1635983,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:23:33.000Z","msg":"有固定位置，<br />\n驚唔驚哨兵手足會容易俾狗咬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:51:22.000Z","msg":"哨兵通常都街坊裝，正常就隱藏得幾好既<br />\n<br />\n同埋個哨點唔一定要好明確係邊棟大廈/邊個涼亭入面<br />\n<br />\n只需要大範圍啲，好似邊個公園或者邊個路口咁 <br />\n<br />\n周圍咁多街坊，應該好容易容入普通市民，冇咁易卑狗咬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"班癲狗而家連街坊都咬，手足小心爲上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}